# Laws

## Army Model

* Barracks = professional army
* Conscripts = recruited from populace

### Disarmed nation (no army)

* No conscripts
* No barracks
* Diplomacy bonuses
* Cultural bonuses

### Only volunteers 

* Little conscripts (like 10 per state)
* No barracks
* Low army bonuses

### Designated Clickers

* Little conscripts
* Little barracks (2 or 3 per state)
* High army bonuses
* Medium army maintenance

### National militia

* Lot of conscripts
* Medium barracks
* Low army bonuses

### Army with a nation

* Little conscripts
* High barracks
* Very high army bonuses
* Very high army maintenance
